Foote Mineral Co said it signed aletter of intent with Shieldalloy Corp, a wholly-ownedsubsidiary of &lt;Metallurg Inc>, for the sale of its Cambridge,Ohio, business.    The company said the sale, which will be explained ingreater detail after the definitive agreement has been signed,is part of Foote's previously-announced plan to sell the entirecompany. Reuter&#3;